Day 2 and 3 was really great, we had our guest speaker Adam Bricker break down how to learn, the mental model, we also talked about atomic habits. We went over 7 essential life skills. Which were Technical skill,discipline,curiosity,collaboration,critical thinking,Grit, Agency under duress, humility,
4 rules to the mental model were, Is it true? Is it timeless? Is it beautiful? Is it the gift I want to give myself?
We also discussed the art of taking breaks and how to take them, I will learn more about the nueroscience behind it outside of class.
To end day 4 Pastor Bruce came in and spoke about his journey and the 4 rules he lives by, be prompt, be prepared, be passionate, be present, and you will perform well.
